name: Experiment Or Die #57
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays layout is a huge shout out to the live action Cowboy Bebop show that just came out on Netflix. The show is savvy and cool, and of course I LOVE the opening credits from a Graphic Designers point of view. Spike Spiegel is just so suave and badass, and todays design is a love letter to this amazing character. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
